txt.en: Thranduil has asked you to scout Parth Daenath.

'We have secured much of Parth Daenath, but Sauron's forces still grasp at the edge of the Corpse-fields. I require more men to patrol and scout Parth Daenath. Once you have done this, report back to me. We must make certain our presence is not forgotten if we are to win this war. Let us remind Sauron that he remains opposed, even after so many years of siege.'
Thranduil requires more knowledge of the Enemies' movements throughout the Corpse-fields of Parth Daenath.
Thranduil can be found at Echad-in-Edhil.\n\nYou should talk to Thranduil.
'You did well in this task, but it was only a start. We are known to the enemy. Now we will take that reminder and turn it into a weapon of fear.'
